g.title: j1171523281
g.text: Arthur, about that Fables & Frontiers game - it'll mean a lot to both Amir and I if you play.

g.title: j4042746030
g.text: Hey, Arthur - I know you already said no to that game of Fables & Frontiers, but I think it'll be fun.

g.title: j1429691087
g.text: Hey, do you want to play Fables & Frontiers with Amir and I? I think it'll be fun.

g.title: j2451570170
g.text: Hey Arthur. Amir is putting together a game of Fables & Frontiers, and it'd mean a lot to both of us if you'd join.

g.title: j778663719
g.text: We have very different definitions of "fun." Sorry, pass.

g.title: j2833996339
g.text: I think it'd be a lot of fun, and a good bonding experience for all of us.

g.title: j1683488599
g.text: He feels like the odd man out - the non-military one, the nerd, kind of on the outside. It'd mean a lot to him if we all sat down and played one of his games with him.

g.title: j3503089915
g.text: Yeah... that's fair. All right, I'll play. Count me in.

g.title: j262748250
g.text: At least for one night, to see how it goes.
